                  Irina Sens is the Deputy Director at the <%= link_to 'German
                  National Library of Science and Technology', 'http://tib.eu'
                  %> (TIB). She led the German project “Registration of
                  Scientific primary data” and was responsible for the
                  introduction of DOI.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
					

					
      </div>
			
			
    </div>
  </div>
